It's getting cancelled.

15
00:01:18,617 --> 00:01:19,950
Kang Yeo Reum.

16
00:01:19,950 --> 00:01:22,683
She's never spilled any details

17
00:01:22,683 --> 00:01:27,083
about what happened on set, our Yeo Reum.

18
00:01:27,083 --> 00:01:29,383
Show some respect

19
00:01:29,383 --> 00:01:31,783
to the people you've worked with.

20
00:01:31,783 --> 00:01:33,683
You scum!

21
00:01:33,683 --> 00:01:35,750
<i>No matter how hard I try,</i>

22
00:01:35,750 --> 00:01:38,550
<i>I can't move forward to the stage.</i>

23
00:01:41,117 --> 00:01:43,650
<i>I wanted to be in the spotlight.</i>

24
00:01:44,550 --> 00:01:47,583
<i>I dreamed of being the main character.</i>

25
00:01:47,583 --> 00:01:49,817
<i>I'm ruined.</i>

26
00:01:58,583 --> 00:02:00,583
Substitute travel?

27
00:02:00,583 --> 00:02:02,383
Since traveling is hard for them,

28
00:02:02,383 --> 00:02:05,917
they want someone to take their
place and show them the experience.

29
00:02:06,950 --> 00:02:08,750
<i>I'd like to travel to Korea,</i>

30
00:02:08,750 --> 00:02:12,850
<i>but for personal reasons, I cannot visit.</i>

31
00:02:12,850 --> 00:02:15,250
Why... Buyeo?

32
00:02:15,250 --> 00:02:17,517
<i>I'm also curious.</i>

33
00:02:28,550 --> 00:02:33,617
'There aren't many Koreans
in Denver where I live.'

34
00:02:33,617 --> 00:02:36,383
'Long ago, I met an exchange student'

35
00:02:36,383 --> 00:02:39,650
'who told me about a place called Buyeo.'

36
00:02:39,650 --> 00:02:43,083
'I never got to visit there myself.'

37
00:02:44,450 --> 00:02:48,250
'I don't know anyone in Korea,'

38
00:02:48,250 --> 00:02:50,683
'but after watching you for five years,'

39
00:02:50,683 --> 00:02:54,450
'Ms. Yeo Reum feels like a close friend.'

40
00:02:55,183 --> 00:02:57,183
'Could you show me'

41
00:02:57,183 --> 00:03:01,317
'what Buyeo is like through videos?'

42
00:03:01,317 --> 00:03:05,350
'Please visit there in my stead.'

43
00:03:12,983 --> 00:03:18,983
[Episode 3 Can Trees Travel Too?]

44
00:03:19,617 --> 00:03:22,117
[Episode 3]

45
00:03:32,750 --> 00:03:34,483
I'll enjoy the food.

46
00:03:34,483 --> 00:03:36,217
Wait a moment.

47
00:03:53,283 --> 00:03:55,083
Kate,

48
00:03:55,850 --> 00:04:01,083
this is lotus leaf rice, a famous local dish here.

49
00:04:01,083 --> 00:04:04,917
They say this place, 'Gungnamji', holds the oldest

50
00:04:04,917 --> 00:04:07,183
royal pond in Korea.

51
00:04:07,183 --> 00:04:09,783
Gungnamji is famous for lotus flowers,

52
00:04:09,783 --> 00:04:11,183
